<span class="flex justify-between md:flex-col items-stretch">
<img data-src="https://i0.wp.com/cms.sofrep.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/07/IMG_1841_opt1.jpg?fit=660%2C495&amp;ssl=1&amp;resize=350%2C200" alt="Building a Precision Sniper Rifle on a Budget | Part 3" class="object-cover w-4/12 h-32 md:w-full md:h-40 order-last md:order-first lazy" />
<div class="content p-5 pl-0 md:px-0 flex flex-col justify-between">
<h3 class="md:text-lg">Building a Precision Sniper Rifle on a Budget | Part 3</h3>
<div class="category-date flex justify-between md:hidden">
<span class="category text-xxs uppercase"></span>
<span class="date text-xxs uppercase">Jan 04</span>
</div>
</div>
</span>
 </a>
</div>
